 Life and the Social Witness of the Church According to Joseph Cardinal Parecattil|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mnM-Oiul2KcC&pg=PA45|date=1 January 1996|publisher=Gregorian Biblical BookShop|isbn=978-88-7652-695-4|pages=45\u2013}}</ref> \u2013 Hindu sage, social reformer\n* [[Chinmayananda Saraswati|Swami Chinmayananda Saraswati]] (born Balakrishna Menon)\n\n==Politicians==\n* [[E. K. Nayanar]]\n* [[Devan Nair|C.V. Devan Nair]], third President of [[Singapore]]\n* [[V.K. Krishna Menon]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hQ8p4XTRZgEC&pg=PT80&dq=himself+of+the+Nair+caste&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj_1cTD7JDKAhVX32MKHY63AW04FBDoAQgbMAA#v=onepage&q=Nair&f=false |title=Nehru: A Contemporary's Estimate |author=Walter Crocker |website=Books.google.com |date= |accessdate=2016-02-24}}</ref>\n* [[Shashi Tharoor]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fRSC_uTGhZ8C&pg=PA114 |title=India: From Midnight to the Millennium and Beyond |first=Shashi |last=Tharoor |page=114 |date=1947-08-15 |accessdate=2016-02-24}}</ref>\n*[[Ambat Sivarama Menon]]\n*[[Paravoor T. K. Narayana Pillai|Paravoor T.K Narayana Pillai]]\n* [[A. K. Gopalan| AKG ]] (AK Gopalan) : communist leader and India's first opposition leader. \n* [[ MGR ]](MG Ramachandran)\n* [[ C Achutha Menon ]] (former Kerala CM)\n* [[ Pattom Thanu Pillai ]](former CM of Travancore-Cochin)\n* [[ C. Sankaran Nair ]] (former president of Indian National Congress)\n* [[ M. V. Raghavan]]\n* [[ O. Rajagopal ]]\n* [[ Prakash Karat ]]\n* [[Ramesh Chennithala]]\n* [[P. Sankaran|P.Sankaran]]\n* [[Rajmohan Unnithan]]\n* [[Kummanam Rajasekharan|Kummanam Rajashekharan]]\n* [[P. Krishna Pillai|P. Krisha Pillai]]\n\n==Policymakers/administrators==\n* [[Raja Kesavadas]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lRkoAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA271&dq=Raja+Kesavadas+Nayar+caste&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiB_8OQscDKAhXIQCYKHVgtCgkQ6AEIHDAA#v=onepage&q=Raja%20Kesavadas%20Nayar%20caste&f=false |title=The New Asiatic Review |