ited Kingdom general election|1966]]\n|128,474\n|5.0\n|{{Composition bar|0|71|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{steady}}\n|{{steady}}\n|{{steady}}\n|{{n/a}}\n|-\n|[[1970 United Kingdom general election|1970]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[William Wolfe]] <br><small>''Candidate in [[West Lothian (UK Parliament constituency)|West Lothian]]''</small>\n|306,802\n|11.4\n|{{Composition bar|1|71|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{increase}} 1\n|{{increase}} 4th\n|{{increase}} 5th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[February 1974 United Kingdom general election|February 1974]]\n|633,180\n|21.9\n|{{Composition bar|7|71|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{increase}} 6\n|{{increase}} 3rd\n|{{increase}} 4th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[October 1974 United Kingdom general election|October 1974]]\n|839,617\n|30.4\n|{{Composition bar|11|71|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{increase}} 4\n|{{steady}} 3rd\n|{{steady}} 4th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[1979 United Kingdom general election|1979]]\n|504,259\n|17.3\n|{{Composition bar|2|71|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{decrease}} 9\n|{{decrease}} 4th\n|{{decrease}} 6th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[1983 United Kingdom general election|1983]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Gordon Wilson (Scottish politician)|Gordon Wilson]] <br><small>MP for [[Dundee East (UK Parliament constituency)|Dundee East]]</small>\n|331,975\n|11.7\n|{{Composition bar|2|72|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{steady}}\n|{{decrease}} 5th\n|{{decrease}} 7th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[1987 United Kingdom general election|1987]]\n|416,473\n|14.0\n|{{Composition bar|3|72|background-color=#DDDDDD|{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n|{{increase}} 1\n|{{increase}} 4th\n|{{increase}} 5th\n|{{no2|Opposition}}\n|-\n|[[1992 United Kingdom general election|1992]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Alex Salmond